  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Golemworks </strong></i>is an experimental fusion of tower defense and factory builder. You must assemble a factory that generates an army of automatons. These automatons automatically fight and defend your golem foundry from waves of encroaching shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/12cc25cd3aa2d9b4edf2a9f0ff9c1e92.poster.avif?t=1773695816\" width=708 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/12cc25cd3aa2d9b4edf2a9f0ff9c1e92.webm?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/12cc25cd3aa2d9b4edf2a9f0ff9c1e92.mp4?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Molds</strong> activate on a cooldown, and generate a golem core - the 'recipe' for an automaton.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/084a7f978c195895b5575abebaf2c477.poster.avif?t=1773695816\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/084a7f978c195895b5575abebaf2c477.webm?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/084a7f978c195895b5575abebaf2c477.mp4?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Catalysts</strong> are the production infrastructure. They can add levels, add elemental attributes, or otherwise alter a core </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/5596dc08a7836a4e01ad5860448d47a0.poster.avif?t=1773695816\" width=520 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/5596dc08a7836a4e01ad5860448d47a0.webm?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/5596dc08a7836a4e01ad5860448d47a0.mp4?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival will hinge on your ability to optimize the strength of your golem army. Good luck.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable golem upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenges and varying difficulties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>All in-game art drawn by hand in Aseprite. Capsule art by @afique_asyraf</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Golemworks </strong></i>is an experimental fusion of tower defense and factory builder. You must assemble a factory that generates an army of automatons. These automatons automatically fight and defend your golem foundry from waves of encroaching shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/12cc25cd3aa2d9b4edf2a9f0ff9c1e92.poster.avif?t=1773695816\" width=708 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/12cc25cd3aa2d9b4edf2a9f0ff9c1e92.webm?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/12cc25cd3aa2d9b4edf2a9f0ff9c1e92.mp4?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Molds</strong> activate on a cooldown, and generate a golem core - the 'recipe' for an automaton.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/084a7f978c195895b5575abebaf2c477.poster.avif?t=1773695816\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/084a7f978c195895b5575abebaf2c477.webm?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/084a7f978c195895b5575abebaf2c477.mp4?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Catalysts</strong> are the production infrastructure. They can add levels, add elemental attributes, or otherwise alter a core </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/5596dc08a7836a4e01ad5860448d47a0.poster.avif?t=1773695816\" width=520 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/5596dc08a7836a4e01ad5860448d47a0.webm?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3918970/extras/5596dc08a7836a4e01ad5860448d47a0.mp4?t=1773695816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival will hinge on your ability to optimize the strength of your golem army. Good luck.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable golem upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenges and varying difficulties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>All in-game art drawn by hand in Aseprite. Capsule art by @afique_asyraf</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
